<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL7">
<l>pulaiyaṟa māki niṉṟa puttoṭu camaṇa mellāṅ</l>
<l>kalaiyaṟak kaṟṟa māntar kāṇparō kēṭpa rōtām</l>
<l>talaiyaṟup puṇṭuñ cāvēṉ cattiyaṅ kāṇmiṉ aiyā</l>
<l>cilaiyiṉā lilaṅkai ceṟṟa tēvaṉē tēva ṉāvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will the people who have thoroughly learnt the Vedas see [or] hear [about]</l>
<l>Jainism—along with Buddhism and all—which are lowly dharmas?</l>
<l>I shall not die even if beheaded! O Sirs, look! It is the truth!</l>
<l>It is the Lord who destroyed Laṅkā by means of [His] bow who is the Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
